<br>
It is going to be interesting to see how they do the next few ones, there is so much material involved.  I mean they have to pull off a major quidditch tournament and the inter school competition too.<br>
<br>
Anyhow, if you haven't seen it yet it's definately one to go see.  Not for little kids though.  There are a couple of monsters that might keep 5 and 6 year olds up at night.<br>
